Falsoyd: Falsoyd's a little shoot-em-up on your desktop.
Falsoyd: Fire at little ships or you die.

About:
Falsoyd is yacwot (yet another complete waste of time) written in c++ using SDL for graphics and sound.

Compiling:
Falsoyd might not compile on your machine. Good luck.
Check the "config" file for some simple options you may want to set.
To compile, just type 'make && make install'.

Controls:
Mouse			Turn the ship
Right mouse button	Thrust
Left mouse button	Fire
Middle mouse button	Special weapon of Doom And Destruction (SWODAD)
p			Pause
ESC			Toggle from menu to game screen
